data.title: About: WHLM (AM)
data.meta_description: WHLM (930 kHz) is an AM radio station broadcasting and licensed to Bloomsburg, Pennsylvania, United States. Until 2022, the station was owned by Columbia Broadcasting Company (not affiliated with CBS Radio). The Columbia Broadcasting Company also owned WBWX (which serves as a satellite station of WHLM), and a second company called Columbia FM Inc., which formerly owned WMMZ. The stations studios are located on East Main Street in downtown Bloomsburg, Pennsylvania.
